      "comment": "LOCKABA NITRO (1) pinged the lids last start from an awkward draw and led throughout to score (19.97) at this track in a Other over 342m. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early off the inside. Looks the one to beat. MY MUM'S VALUE (2) has good speed and can quickly clear the draw. Last start finished 3rd over 342m at this track beaten 4 lengths (20.30) behind South King in a Other on April 28. Suited here and expected to run well. ANTECEDENT (5) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 19.93 beating On The Strip. One of the prime contenders. DISTRICTS DUB (8) scored from box 8 last start – cannot be left out of calculations.",
